The paper also discusses the problem of hidden stratification, which is a statistical issue, and the techniques used to measure and describe it, which suggests that it could also belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with medical imaging datasets, which suggests that it could belong to the Medical Imaging (cs.MED) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the clinical implications of the findings, which suggests that it could also belong to the Clinical Applications (cs.CL) sub-category.
